{
  "stem": "25598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But their life was a lot more primitive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- it was communism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lived in so-called capitalism and monarchy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our life was more advanced, so to speak, materially.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived in a lot more primitive conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were shoved into the huts with, with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of the men had been taken to the Russian army, so the population we found there were women, old men, old women, and kids.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So on this barge when the crossed the Dniester, I happened to be standing beside this woman who was in our car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was holding the baby in one arm and the bundle of, I don't know, blankets or diapers or whatever-- of [GERMAN] in the other hand.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was staring into the waves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at some point she dropped the baby in the waves, and there wasn't a sound from her or from anybody else.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother, who was in the back of me, said to my father, look at what animals we became only in a few days.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody's jumping in to get the baby.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- it was-- we never found out if she wanted to dump the baby or if she wanted to dump the bundle because it was to heavy for her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody moved, nobody screamed, nobody said, oh, my god.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Look what's happening.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the train when people died-- and there were people who died in the boxcar-- that is when I encountered death and saw dead people for the first time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I didn't know that they were dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I thought they were asleep, even though their faces change when they're dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was wondering how come their faces change when they're asleep.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
